            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指跌64點報26098點 華勤技術高開12.68%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段未能跟隨外圍造好，在競價時段進一步下調。恒生指數開市報26098點，跌64點或0.25%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4962點，蹤點或0.04%；國企指數以8799點開市，跌2點或0.03%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股互有升跌，據報獲洽談投資DeepSeek(深度求索)的阿里巴巴(09988)與騰訊(00700)，股價在競價時段個別發展；阿里巴巴開報132.6元，升0.84%；騰訊開報500元，跌0.79%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩大藍籌國際金融股方面，滙控(00005)開報142元，跌1.39%；友邦(01299)開報82.05元，跌1.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)昨天捱沽後，今早開報699元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">業績股方面，金沙中國(01928)首季成績表今早出爐後股價受壓，開報17.13元，暫時無升跌；新東方(09901)績後股價於今早開報43.58元，同樣暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華勤技術(03296)今早掛牌，以 元開市，較招股價77.7元高12.68%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909221-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c64%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126098%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8f%af%e5%8b%a4%e6%8a%80%e8%a1%93%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b12",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 09:28:03",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
